      <title>特朗普发出关税威胁，白宫计划改革贸易政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/as-trump-lobs-tariff-threats-white-house-maps-trade-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普回到白宫的头 36 个小时里，他就威胁最早从下周开始对美国前四大贸易伙伴征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/as-trump-lobs-tariff-threats-white-house-maps-trade-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 18:07:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将贩毒集团列为恐怖分子 银行陷入危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-s-terrorist-label-for-cartels-is-putting-banks-on-edge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将墨西哥贩毒集团列为恐怖组织，这可能会对金融公司和其他公司产生寒蝉效应，因为他们担心，即使是在不知情的情况下为犯罪分子提供服务或支付费用，也可能面临严厉的惩罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-s-terrorist-label-for-cartels-is-putting-banks-on-edge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:58:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克和奥特曼就特朗普大肆宣传的 100 亿美元人工智能项目发生争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/musk-says-firms-backing-trump-ai-initiative-don-t-have-the-money</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克公开质疑那些加入唐纳德·特朗普总统承诺投资数千亿美元用于人工智能基础设施建设的公司是否能够兑现承诺，这暴露了白宫内部早期的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/musk-says-firms-backing-trump-ai-initiative-don-t-have-the-money</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:50:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普批准减税，SALT 谈判升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/salt-talks-gain-steam-in-congress-as-trump-blesses-expanding-tax-break</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在赢得总统唐纳德·特朗普和国会领导人的承诺后，众议院共和党人正在就提高州和地方税减免上限进行谈判，将该措施纳入今年必须通过的税收法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/salt-talks-gain-steam-in-congress-as-trump-blesses-expanding-tax-break</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:38:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国持刀袭击致两人死亡，其中包括一名两岁儿童</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/two-dead-in-german-knife-attack-including-two-year-old-child</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国阿沙芬堡市发生一起持刀袭击事件，造成两人死亡，其中包括一名两岁儿童，这是下个月提前大选前一系列致命事件中的最新一起，引发了有关国内安全和移民问题的争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/two-dead-in-german-knife-attack-including-two-year-old-child</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:37:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙和肖尔茨组成统一阵线应对特朗普威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/macron-scholz-project-united-front-in-face-of-trump-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对唐纳德·特朗普总统破坏跨大西洋关系的威胁，埃马纽埃尔·马克龙和奥拉夫·朔尔茨周三呼吁欧洲团结起来，打造更强大、更具竞争力的欧洲工业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/macron-scholz-project-united-front-in-face-of-trump-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:17:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰部长称愿意帮助保险公司投资国防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/dutch-willing-to-help-insurers-invest-in-defense-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长鲁本·布雷克曼斯表示，荷兰保险公司和其他希望投资国防工业的金融机构可以期待政府的指导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/dutch-willing-to-help-insurers-invest-in-defense-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普会晤后，Stellantis 大力宣传其在美国的工厂投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/stellantis-touts-us-factory-investments-days-after-meeting-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了讨好唐纳德·特朗普总统，吉普运动型多用途车制造商 Stellantis NV 正在重新承诺履行一年多前达成的在美国工厂的投资协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/stellantis-touts-us-factory-investments-days-after-meeting-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:15:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普司法部官员为打击移民奠定基础</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/top-trump-doj-official-lays-groundwork-for-immigration-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[司法部员工被告知要支持唐纳德·特朗普的移民议程，与联邦移民执法人员分享收集到的非法入境人员的数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/top-trump-doj-official-lays-groundwork-for-immigration-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 12:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
